    </sec>
    <sec id="sec4">
      <title>Discussion</title>
      <p>The enhanced output pipeline provides a robust solution for document conversion in scholarly publishing. By generating multiple formats from a single source, we enable flexibility in downstream processing while maintaining high standards of compliance and quality.</p>
      <p>Key advantages include:</p>
      <list list-type="simple">
        <list-item>
          <p>Automated validation at each stage</p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>Preservation of original formatting in direct PDF</p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>Standards compliance for archival and indexing</p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>Comprehensive unit testing</p>
        </list-item>
      </list>
    </sec>
    <sec id="sec5">
      <title>Conclusion</title>
      <p>The enhanced output pipeline successfully addresses the challenges of modern scholarly document conversion. Future work will focus on expanding format support and improving AI-powered content repair capabilities.</p>
